531 
532 THE CHRISTMAS TREES
533 
534 
535 On the high slope of Going-To-The-Sun
536 Is a stormy Christmas, all year round,
537 And snow-filled Christmas trees abound.
538 
539 [Illustration: VACHEL LINDSAY, 1922]
