1357 THE LAND HORSE AND THE SEA HORSE
1358 
1359 
1360 The Land Horse
1361 Everybody rides,
1362 Until his eyes are dim.
1363 
1364 [Illustration: THE LAND HORSE]
1365 
1366 [Illustration]
1367 
1368 The Sea Horse!
1369 Every wave he rides.
1370 And nobody
1371 Rides him.
